Your main issue was related to the use of `Scanner`.

 1. For titles, since they can have more than one word (separated with spaces), you needed to use `Scanner#nextLine()` rather than `Scanner#next()`. Because of that,
 2. When you were getting the numeric input for the main menu, you needed to consume the line. Calling `Scanner#nextInt()` doesn&#39;t consume the line. Therefore, you need to call `Scanner#nextLine()` before the next prompt so that the scanner is moved to the next line to get the next inputted value.

